data.description: Welcome home to Sandtrap Road!  This charming brick home is tucked away on a quiet street in the Corey Woods subdivision in Summerville and is a must see!   An entry hall welcomes you into the home with the living area on your left and the home's three bedrooms and two full bathrooms down the hall to your right. The living room, dining room and kitchen are spacious and open to one another and feature great natural light. The kitchen features a large peninsula with room for seating and tons of cabinetry and counterspace. Through the living room you will find the entrance to your large, fully fenced in and private yard with mature oaks.  Off of the living room you will find your laundry room, entrance to the FROG (finished room over the garage with walk up attic storage) and your sizable two car garage. The FROG is a perfect flex space and can be used to fit your needs as a playroom, an office, a gym...the possibilities are endless!  Head through the living area and down the hall to find three sizable bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The owner's suite features its own bathroom.  This peaceful and family friendly community is highly sought after and features great walkability and with no HOA or flood insurance required, this is an amazing find!
